%h1 Flatland Competition

%h2 Competitor Order

%p
  The Event Director can configure the order in which competitors are expected to compete

= image_tag "screenshots/flatland_order.png", class: "screenshot"

%h2 Manage Judges

%p
  The Event director can configure a number of judge users who will be able to enter results

= image_tag "screenshots/flatland_judge_selection.png", class: "screenshot"

%h2 Enter Judging Results

%p
  Each Judge will be able to enter results for all competitors.

= image_tag "screenshots/flatland_judge_data_entry_1.png", class: "screenshot"
= image_tag "screenshots/flatland_judge_data_entry_2.png", class: "screenshot"

%h2 Results Monitoring

%p
  The Event Director can monitor the number of results entered by each judge

= image_tag "screenshots/flatland_judge_data_monitoring.png", class: "screenshot"
= image_tag "screenshots/flatland_judge_data_monitoring_details.png", class: "screenshot"

- if @event.present?
  %p
    - params = { "competition[scoring_class]" => "Flatland IUF 2019", "competition[num_members_per_competitor]" => "One" }
    = link_to "Click here", new_event_competition_path(@event, params), class: "button"
    to continue setting up your Flatland Competition.
